title: This service is only available to users over a certain age
quoteText: To use our Services or become a “User” (as defined below), you agree that you can enter into a binding contract with Kongregate and that you are not a Child. “Child” or “Children” means anyone under the age of 13 (or under 16 in certain European countries).
